    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Variable M Differential Lock, this chassis provides exceptional longitudinal and lateral dynamics. The vehicle is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable damping characteristics. Recent preventative maintenance includes upgraded throttle actuators and a thorough inspection of the rod bearings and VANOS system. While showing minor signs of use typical for its age, the mechanical integrity remains robust, offering a visceral driving experience with a rigid subframe and a highly communicative steering rack. A true driver\u2019s specification ready for technical B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
